This is an updated version of the offical socialshareprivay (v1.4) code from:
http://www.heise.de/extras/socialshareprivacy/

+ Additional support for Vkontakte (enabled vkontakte breaks https tests from browsers, vkontakte loads internally an a script via http instead of https)
+ Update all other share buttons to use https links instead of the previously used http urls/iframes

